===Family rides===
Cedar Point has 11 family rides; the newest, [[Dinosaurs Alive! (attraction)|Dinosaurs Alive!]], opened in 2012.<ref name="Family rides">{{cite news |title=Cedar Point Things To Do - Family rides |url=http://www.cedarpoint.com/things-to-do/family-rides| accessdate=June 21, 2012}}</ref>
